# infra/terraform.tfvars holds your deployment-specific config (domain,
# hosted-zone ID, AWS account ID in the OIDC ARN). It's untracked so forks
# start from terraform.tfvars.example and nobody publishes their own account
# identifiers. Copy the .example to terraform.tfvars and fill in your values.
infra/terraform.tfvars

